              Hash: 0x7f9fade1c0d57a7af66ab4ead79fade1c0d57a7
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <strong>Quality Control</strong><br>
              Date: Jan 16, 2024<br>
              Status: Passed all tests<br>
              Hash: 0x8a1bcde2d1e68b8bg77bc5fbe8afade2d1e68b8
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <strong>Distribution Center</strong><br>
              Date: Jan 18, 2024<br>
              Location: MedDist Warehouse, Pennsylvania<br>
              Temp: 2-8¬∞C maintained<br>
              Hash: 0x9b2cdef3e2f79c9ch88cd6gfc9bgbde3e2f79c9
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <strong>Pharmacy Receipt</strong><br>
